    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>North Korea State Sponsor of Terrorism Designation Act of 2017</strong></p> <p>This bill expresses the sense of Congress that the government of North Korea should be designated as a state sponsor of terrorism.</p> <p>The Department of State shall submit to Congress a determination as to whether North Korea meets the criteria for designation as a state sponsor of terrorism.</p>]]></text>
